_:genid7 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#members> _:genid11 .
_:genid11 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid11 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <http://modellingdh.github.io/ont/odp/term/Engagement> .
